          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " and shipped there. Then it was transported to Leicester, England and used as a wedding car couples could rent. Sandham purchased it in 2018 and obviously cares a great deal about it.",
